overview: TransWorld Motocross's Premix 2: Two-Stroke Fever is the long-overdue sequel to the 2015 TransWorld Motocross smash, Premix. Featuring the stars of our sport aboard "vintage" two-stroke motocross bikes, Premix 2 gives viewers what they want to see: raw action, two-stroke sounds, and exhaust smoke that you can practically smell.
